Solution_Comment__c:
Symptom

Reference cases 00429711 & 0042434. Finally have seek jobs where i want them. See the results in the seek bulk import job. When i go to run the job to produce the report (spreadsheet) i am not getting any data within the report.

Cause

FSDLP report was targeting the incorrect view. 

Resolution

Created a new report under the SEEK Bulk Import job targeting the FSDLP_MatchesView table to generate a report with the desired information. Created a report using the process listed in the documentation below:

https://helpcenter.netwrix.com/bundle/EnterpriseAuditor_11.6/page/Content/EnterpriseAuditor/Admin/Report/Create.htm
